@startuml
title 应用设置界面 - 展示配置项并实时保存

actor 用户
participant "SettingsActivity" as Activity
participant "SettingsViewModel" as VM
participant "AppPreferences" as Prefs

用户 -> Activity: 点击“设置”
Activity -> Activity: setContent { SettingsScreen }
Activity -> VM: viewModel(factory)
VM -> Prefs: 读取各配置项的 Flow
Prefs --> VM: 发射当前值
VM --> Activity: 暴露 StateFlow
Activity --> 用户: 显示 UI (TextField, Slider, Switch)
用户 -> Activity: 修改某项配置
Activity -> VM: 调用 updateXxx(newValue)
VM -> Prefs: 调用 setXxx(dataStore, newValue)
Prefs -> Prefs: 持久化
Prefs --> VM: 完成
VM --> Activity: 更新 UI 状态
Activity --> 用户: 显示新值
@enduml
